  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This experiment is designed for post marketing data collection of a cryosurgical system
      [PROSENSE™ of IceCure Medical], for the treatment of renal cell carcinoma (RCC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
